General.Name: AP Acquisition Corp
General.Description: AP Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses in the de-carbonization/renewable energy sectors with a focus in Japan/Asia (excluding China) and European markets. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Singapore.
